                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <p>Start by creating categories. Categories have a few fields, however, only the title and the slug are mandatory. The slug will be used as the category's permalink. Ex: yourShop/knowledge-page/category-page.</p>
                                <p><b>NOTE!</b> Permalinks are useful for SEO.<br />
                                <b>NOTE!</b> You can also edit the slug/Permalink.<br />
                                <b>NOTE!</b> In order to show up within your store front-end, categories must be published.</p>
