                                    <br />
                                    In order to show in front-end, an article must be assigned to a category and published.
                                </p>
                                <p><b>NOTE!</b> Permalinks are useful for SEO.<br />
                                <b>NOTE!</b> You can also edit the slug/Permalink.</p>
