                            </div>
                            <!-- end col -->
                        </div>
                        <!-- end row -->

                        <ul style="list-style-type: none;">
                            <li><h3>1. Go to your Shopify admin area, click "Online Shop" > "Navigation" > "Main menu".</h3></li>
                            <li><h3>2. Click "Add menu item".</h3></li>
                            <li><h3>3. Edit menu item name, paste the link to the knowledge base, click "Add", then click "Save menu".</h3></li>
